articles.author: Jason Rainbow
articles.title: SpaceX launches latest SES broadcast satellite - SpaceNews
articles.description: SpaceX successfully launched Astra 1P for Luxembourg fleet operator SES June 20 toward geostationary orbit, where it is eventually due to replace four older broadcast satellites over Europe.
